description:
This the full version of MD YouTube Downloader v1.1.

I expect someone will tell you what the serial code is, but just for
your information it&amp;#039;s free from the site as mentioned below.

The settings page is missing and so by default all downloaded files go,
directly to your desktop. Check for updates on www.mdmultimedia.co.uk

There is a free serial code on the website, I am not encouraging you to
visit any of the adverts on the site, but please notice that they are
there and visit them if their products interest you, thanks.

Essentially if you take a URL from youtube, for example:

Paste it in to the top of this application, click on the add button
then it will download it to your desktop as a raw FLV file. You are
able to play this with several applications, I recommend VLC from
www.videolan.org, others that have been recommended which I havent
